text: 2077 (MMLXXVII) will be . == Events == * May 15: 150th anniversary of the Hollywood Roosevelt Hotel. * May 18: 150th anniversary of the Grauman's Chinese Theatre. * May 25: 100th anniversary of the Star Wars. * An annular solar eclipse will occur at the Moon's descending node of orbit on Monday, November 15, 2077. ==References== Category:2070s
